title: 233: Week 11 Game Previews, Who's Better: Gurley or Bell?
itunes:title: 233: Week 11 Game Previews, Who's Better: Gurley or Bell?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the biggest games in Week 11 (10:10) and debate which running back is better: the Rams' Todd Gurley or the Steelers' Le'Veon Bell (21:20). The guys also discuss whether UCLA's Josh Rosen or USC's Sam Darnold is the better NFL quarterback prospect (28:10) before making their college football picks (33:00).
